trans-unit.source: Power BI reports for subscription billing
trans-unit.target: Power BI izveštaji za fakturisanje pretplate
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action PBI Reports - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action PBI Reports - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Billing Schedule report provides a forecast of vendor and customer invoiced amounts according to the contractual billing rhythm. It helps to identify future development of incoming and outgoing cash from billed subscriptions.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Raspored fakturisanja” daje prognozu fakturisanih iznosa dobavljača i kupaca, u skladu sa ugovorenim ritmom fakturisanja. Pomaže da se sagleda buduće kretanje priliva i odliva novca po fakturisanim pretplatama.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Billing Schedule (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Billing Schedule (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Churn Analysis report breaks down churn by various dimensions such as contract term, contract type or product.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Analiza odliva” razlaže odliv po različitim dimenzijama, kao što su trajanje ugovora, tip ugovora ili proizvod.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Churn Analysis (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Churn Analysis (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Customer Deferrals report provides an overview of deferred vs. released subscription sales amount.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Razgraničenja kupaca” daje pregled razgraničenog i razknjiženog iznosa prodaje od pretplata.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Customer Deferrals (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Customer Deferrals (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Revenue Analysis report breaks down Monthly Recurring Revenue by various dimension such as billing rhythm, contract type or customer.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Analiza prihoda” razlaže mesečni periodični prihod od pretplata po različitim dimenzijama, kao što su ritam fakturisanja, tip ugovora ili kupac.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue Analysis (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue Analysis (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Revenue by Customer report breaks down subscription performance by customer and item, highlighting metrics such as Monthly Recurring Revenue, Monthly Recurring Cost, Monthly Net Profit Amount and Monthly Net Profit %. This report provides detailed insights into which customers and items are driving subscription revenue and profitability.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Prihod po kupcu” razlaže učinak pretplata po kupcu i artiklu, ističući pokazatelje kao što su mesečni periodični prihod, mesečni periodični trošak, iznos mesečne neto dobiti i procenat mesečne neto dobiti. Ovaj izveštaj pruža detaljan uvid u to koji kupci i artikli najviše doprinose prihodu od pretplata i profitabilnosti.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue by Customer (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue by Customer (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Revenue by Item report breaks down subscription performance by item category, highlighting metrics such as Monthly Recurring Revenue, Monthly Recurring Cost, Monthly Net Profit Amount and Monthly Net Profit %. This report provides detailed insights into which categories and items are driving subscription revenue and profitability.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Prihod po artiklu” razlaže učinak pretplata po kategoriji artikla, ističući pokazatelje kao što su mesečni periodični prihod, mesečni periodični trošak, iznos mesečne neto dobiti i procenat mesečne neto dobiti. Ovaj izveštaj pruža detaljan uvid u to koje kategorije i koji artikli najviše doprinose prihodu od pretplata i profitabilnosti.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue by Item (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue by Item (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Revenue by Salesperson report breaks down subscription performance by Salesperson, highlighting metrics such as Monthly Recurring Revenue, Monthly Recurring Cost, Monthly Net Profit Amount and Churn.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Prihod po prodavcu” razlaže učinak pretplata po prodavcu, ističući pokazatelje kao što su mesečni periodični prihod, mesečni periodični trošak, iznos mesečne neto dobiti i odliv.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue by Salesperson (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue by Salesperson (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Revenue Development report shows the change in monthly recurring revenue and helps to identify its various sources such as churn, downgrades, new subscriptions or upgrades.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Razvoj prihoda" prikazuje promenu mesečnog periodičnog prihoda i pomaže da se prepoznaju njegovi različiti izvori, kao što su odliv, smanjenje paketa, nove pretplate ili nadogradnje.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue Development (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue Development (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Revenue YoY report compares Monthly Recurring Revenue performance across a year-over-year period.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Prihod po godinama" upoređuje učinak mesečnog periodičnog prihoda iz godine u godinu.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue YoY (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Revenue YoY (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Sales and Cost forecast report provides the forecast of Monthly Recurring Revenue and Monthly Recurring Cost for the future months and years. This report provides detailed insights into which salespersons and customers are driving future subscription performance.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Prognoza prodaje i troškova" daje prognozu mesečnog periodičnog prihoda i mesečnog periodičnog troška za naredne mesece i godine. Ovaj izveštaj pruža detaljan uvid u to koji prodavci i kupci najviše doprinose budućem učinku pretplata.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Sales and Cost forecast (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Sales and Cost forecast (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Subscription Billing Report offers a consolidated view of all subscription report pages, conveniently embedded into a single page for easy access.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj o fakturisanju pretplate pruža objedinjeni prikaz svih izveštajnih stranica za pretplate, praktično objedinjenih na jednoj stranici radi lakšeg pristupa.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Subscription Billing Report (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Subscription Billing Report (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Subscription Overview provides a comprehensive view of subscription performance, offering insights into metrics such as Monthly Recurring Revenue, Total Contract Value, Churn and top-performing customers or vendors.
trans-unit.target: Pregled pretplate pruža sveobuhvatan uvid u učinak pretplata, nudeći informacije o pokazateljima kao što su mesečni periodični prihod, ukupna vrednost ugovora, odliv i najuspešniji kupci ili dobavljači.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Subscription Overview (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Subscription Overview (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Total Contract Value Analysis report breaks down Total Contract Value by various dimension such as billing rhythm, contract type or customer.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Analiza ukupne vrednosti ugovora" razlaže ukupnu vrednost ugovora po različitim dimenzijama, kao što su ritam fakturisanja, tip ugovora ili kupac.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Total Contract Value Analysis (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Total Contract Value Analysis (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Total Contract Value YoY report compares the Total Contract Value and Active Customers across a year-over-year period.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Ukupna vrednost ugovora po godinama" upoređuje ukupnu vrednost ugovora i broj aktivnih kupaca iz godine u godinu.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Total Contract Value YoY (Power BI) - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.target: Ukupna vrednost ugovora po godinama (Power BI)
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Total Contract Value YoY (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: The Vendor Deferrals report provides an overview of deferred vs. released subscription cost amount.
trans-unit.target: Izveštaj "Razgraničenja dobavljača" daje pregled razgraničenog i razknjiženog iznosa troška pretplate.
trans-unit.note: PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Vendor Deferrals (Power BI) - Property ToolTip
PageExtension Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Vendor Deferrals (Power BI) - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Detailed information on Customer Subscription Contracts that include recurring subscriptions. A Customer Subscription Contract is used to calculate these Subscription Lines based on the parameters specified in the Subscription Lines. The Subscription Lines are presented in detail and can be edited. In addition, commercial information as well as delivery and billing addresses can be stored in a Contract.
trans-unit.target: Detaljne informacije o pretplatničkim ugovorima sa kupcima koji uključuju ponavljajuće pretplate. Pretplatnički ugovor za kupca se koristi za izračunavanje pretplatničkih redova na osnovu parametara navedenih u pretplatničkim redovima. Pretplatničke redovi su detaljno predstavljeni i mogu se uređivati. Pored toga, komercijalne informacije, kao i adrese za isporuku i fakturisanje mogu se čuvati u ugovoru.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action CustomerContractsList - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action CustomerContractsList - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: View or edit detailed information for the customers that you trade with. From each customer card, you can open related information, such as sales statistics and ongoing orders, and you can define special prices and line discounts that you grant if certain conditions are met.
trans-unit.target: Prikažite ili uredite detaljne informacije o kupcima sa kojima poslujete. Sa svake kartice kupca možete otvoriti povezane informacije, kao što su prodajna statistika i tekuće porudžbine, i definisati posebne cene i popuste na red koje odobravate kada su ispunjeni određeni uslovi.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action CustomersList - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action CustomersList - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: View or edit detailed information for the products that you trade in. The item card can be of type Inventory or Service to specify if the item is a physical unit or a labor time unit. Here you also define if items in inventory or on incoming orders are automatically reserved for outbound documents and whether order tracking links are created between demand and supply to reflect planning actions.
trans-unit.target: Prikažite ili uredite detaljne informacije o proizvodima kojima trgujete. Kartica artikla može biti tipa Zaliha ili Servis da bi se navelo da li je artikal fizička jedinica ili jedinica radnog vremena. Ovde takođe određujete da li se artikli na zalihama ili na ulaznim porudžbinama automatski rezervišu za izlazne dokumente i da li se kreiraju veze praćenja porudžbina između potražnje i ponude radi odražavanja planiranih akcija.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action ItemsList - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action ItemsList - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Define a project activity by creating a project card with integrated project tasks and project planning lines, structured in two layers. The project task enables you to set up project planning lines and to post consumption to the project. The project planning lines specify the detailed use of resources, items, and various general ledger expenses.
trans-unit.target: Definišite projektnu aktivnost kreiranjem kartice projekta sa integrisanim projektnim zadacima i projektnim planiranim redovima, strukturisanim u dva nivoa. Projektni zadatak vam omogućava da postavite projektne planirane redove i knjižite utrošak na projekat. Projektni planirani redovi preciziraju detaljnu upotrebu resursa, artikala i raznih troškova glavne knjige.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action JobsList - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action JobsList - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Detailed information on the Subscriptions. The Subscriptions shows the item for which it was created and the Subscription Lines that belong to it. The amount and the details of the provision can be seen. The service recipient indicates to which customer the Subscription Item was sold. Different delivery and billing addresses provide information about who the item was delivered to and who received the invoice. In addition, the Subscription Lines are shown in detail and can be edited.
trans-unit.target: Detaljne informacije o pretplatama. Pretplate prikazuju artikal za koji je kreirana i pretplatničke redove koje joj pripadaju. Mogu se videti iznos i detalji pretplate. Primalac usluge označava kojem kupcu je prodata stavka pretplate. Različite adrese za isporuku i fakturisanje pružaju informacije o tome kome je predmet isporučen i ko je primio fakturu. Pored toga, redovi za pretplatu su detaljno prikazane i mogu se uređivati.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action ServiceObjectsList - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action ServiceObjectsList - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Detailed information on Vendor Subscription Contracts that include recurring subscriptions. A Vendor Subscription Contract is used to calculate these Subscription Lines based on the parameters specified in the Subscription Lines. trans-unit.target: Detaljne informacije o pretplatničkim ugovorima sa dobavljačima koji obuhvataju ponavljajuće pretplate. Pretplatnički ugovor sa dobavljačem koristi se za izračunavanje redova pretplate na osnovu parametara navedenih u redovima pretplate. Redovi pretplate su prikazani detaljno i mogu se uređivati. Pored toga, u ugovoru se mogu čuvati komercijalne informacije.

trans-unit.source: Create purchase credit memos to mirror sales credit memos that vendors send to you for incorrect or damaged items that you have paid for and then returned to the vendor. If you need more control of the purchase return process, such as warehouse documents for the physical handling, use purchase return orders, in which purchase credit memos are integrated. Purchase credit memos can be created automatically from PDF or image files from your vendors by using the Incoming Documents feature. Note: If you have not yet paid for an erroneous purchase, you can simply cancel the posted purchase invoice to automatically revert the financial transaction.
trans-unit.target: Kreirajte nabavna odobrenja da biste ispratili prodajna odobrenja koja vam dobavljači šalju za pogrešne ili oštećene artikle koje ste platili, a potom vratili dobavljaču. Ako vam je potrebna veća kontrola procesa povraćaja u nabavci (npr. magacinski dokumenti za fizičko rukovanje), koristite naloge za povraćaj u nabavci, u koje su integrisana nabavna odobrenja. Nabavna odobrenja mogu biti automatski kreirana iz PDF ili slikovnih fajlova vaših dobavljača pomoću funkcionalnosti Ulazni dokumenti. Napomena: Ako još niste platili pogrešnu nabavku, možete jednostavno stornirati proknjiženu nabavnu fakturu da bi se finansijska transakcija automatski vratila.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action PurchaseCreditMemos - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action PurchaseCreditMemos - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Create purchase invoices to mirror sales documents that vendors send to you. This enables you to record the cost of purchases and to track accounts payable. Posting purchase invoices dynamically updates inventory levels so that you can minimize inventory costs and provide better customer service. Purchase invoices can be created automatically from PDF or image files from your vendors by using the Incoming Documents feature.
trans-unit.target: Kreirajte nabavne fakture kao odraz prodajnih dokumenata koje vam šalju dobavljači. Ovo vam omogućava da evidentirate trošak nabavke i pratite obaveze prema dobavljačima. Knjiženje nabavnih faktura dinamički ažurira nivoe zaliha kako biste smanjili troškove zaliha i obezbedili bolju uslugu kupcima. Nabavne fakture mogu biti automatski kreirane iz PDF ili slikovnih fajlova vaših dobavljača pomoću funkcionalnosti Ulazni dokumenti.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action PurchaseInvoices - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action PurchaseInvoices - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Create purchase orders to mirror sales documents that vendors send to you. This enables you to record the cost of purchases and to track accounts payable. Posting purchase orders dynamically updates inventory levels so that you can minimize inventory costs and provide better customer service. Purchase orders allow partial receipts, unlike with purchase invoices, and enable drop shipment directly from your vendor to your customer. Purchase orders can be created automatically from PDF or image files from your vendors by using the Incoming Documents feature.
trans-unit.target: Kreirajte nabavne porudžbine kao odraz prodajnih dokumenata koje vam šalju dobavljači. Time evidentirate trošak nabavki i pratite obaveze prema dobavljačima. Knjiženje nabavnih porudžbina dinamički ažurira zalihe kako biste smanjili troškove i pružili bolju uslugu. Nabavne porudžbine omogućavaju delimične prijeme (za razliku od nabavnih faktura) i drop shipment direktno od dobavljača ka kupcu. Porudžbine se mogu automatski kreirati iz PDF/slikovnih fajlova pomoću funkcije Ulazni dokumenti.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action PurchaseOrders - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action PurchaseOrders - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Make offers to customers to sell certain products on certain delivery and payment terms. While you negotiate with a customer, you can change and resend the sales quote as much as needed. When the customer accepts the offer, you convert the sales quote to a sales invoice or a sales order in which you process the sale.
trans-unit.target: Dajte ponude kupcima za prodaju određenih proizvoda pod tačno definisanim uslovima isporuke i plaćanja. Tokom pregovora sa kupcem možete menjati i ponovo slati prodajnu ponudu koliko je potrebno. Kada kupac prihvati ponudu, konvertujete je u prodajnu fakturu ili prodajnu porudžbinu u kojoj obrađujete prodaju.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Sales Quotes - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action Sales Quotes - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Revert the financial transactions involved when your customers want to cancel a purchase or return incorrect or damaged items that you sent to them and received payment for. To include the correct information, you can create the sales credit memo from the related posted sales invoice or you can create a new sales credit memo with copied invoice information. If you need more control of the sales return process, such as warehouse documents for the physical handling, use sales return orders, in which sales credit memos are integrated. Note: If an erroneous sale has not been paid yet, you can simply cancel the posted sales invoice to automatically revert the financial transaction.
trans-unit.target: Vratite finansijske transakcije kada kupci žele da otkažu kupovinu ili vrate pogrešne/oštećene artikle koje ste isporučili i naplatili. Radi tačnosti, možete kreirati prodajno odobrenje iz povezane proknjižene prodajne fakture ili napraviti novo prodajno odobrenje kopiranjem podataka sa fakture. Ako vam treba veća kontrola procesa povraćaja u prodaji (npr. magacinski dokumenti), koristite naloge za povraćaj u prodaji, u koje su prodajna odobrenja integrisana. Napomena: Ako pogrešna prodaja još nije plaćena, možete jednostavno stornirati proknjiženu prodajnu fakturu da se transakcija automatski vrati.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action SalesCreditMemos - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action SalesCreditMemos - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Register your sales to customers and invite them to pay according to the delivery and payment terms by sending them a sales invoice document. Posting a sales invoice registers shipment and records an open receivable entry on the customer's account, which will be closed when payment is received. To manage the shipment process, use sales orders, in which sales invoicing is integrated.
trans-unit.target: Evidentirajte prodaju kupcima i pozovite ih na plaćanje u skladu sa uslovima isporuke i plaćanja slanjem prodajne fakture. Knjiženje prodajne fakture evidentira isporuku i otvara potraživanje na računu kupca, koje se zatvara po prijemu uplate. Za upravljanje procesom isporuke koristite prodajne porudžbine, u koje je fakturisanje integrisano.
trans-unit.note: Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action SalesInvoices - Property ToolTip
Page Sub. Billing Role Center - Action SalesInvoices - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Record your agreements with customers to sell certain products on certain delivery and payment terms. Sales orders, unlike sales invoices, allow you to ship partially, deliver directly from your vendor to your customer, initiate warehouse handling, and print various customer-facing documents. Sales invoicing is integrated in the sales order process.
trans-unit.target: Beleži dogovore sa kupcima o prodaji određenih proizvoda pod tačno definisanim uslovima isporuke i plaćanja. Prodajne porudžbine, za razliku od prodajnih faktura, omogućavaju delimičnu isporuku, direktnu isporuku od dobavljača kupcu, pokretanje skladišnog rukovanja i štampanje raznih dokumenata za kupce. Prodajno fakturisanje je integrisano u proces prodajne porudžbine.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the period in which the entry is evaluated.
trans-unit.target: Određuje period u kome se stavka vrednuje.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Analysis Date - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies for which period the Amount is valid. If you enter 1M here, a period of one month, or 12M, a period of 1 year, to which Amount refers to.
trans-unit.target: Određuje period na koji se iznos odnosi Ako ovde unesete 1M, period važi mesec dana, ako unesete 12M, period važi jednu godinu.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Billing Base Period - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the Dateformula for rhythm in which the Subscription Line is invoiced. Using a Dateformula rhythm can be, for example, a monthly, a quarterly or a yearly invoicing.
trans-unit.target: Određuje formulu datuma za ritam fakturisanja reda pretplate. Pomoću formule datuma ritam može podrazumevati, na primer, mesečno, kvartalno ili godišnje fakturisanje.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Billing Rhythm - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the percent at which the price of the Subscription Line will be calculated. 100% means that the price corresponds to the Base Price.
trans-unit.target: Određuje procenat po kome će se računati cena reda pretplate. Vrednost 100% znači da cena odgovara osnovnoj ceni.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Calculation Base % - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the base amount from which the price will be calculated.
trans-unit.target: Određuje osnovni iznos po kojem će se izračunati cena.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Calculation Base Amount - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the basis on which the price is calculated in client currency.
trans-unit.target: Određuje osnovu na kojoj se cena obračunava u valuti klijenta.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Calculation Base Amount (LCY) - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the last date for a timely termination. The date is determined by the initial term, extension term and a notice period. An initial term of 12 months and a 3-month notice period means that the deadline for a notice of termination is after 9 months. An extension period of 12 months postpones this date by 12 months.
trans-unit.target: Određuje poslednji datum za blagovremeni otkaz. Datum se određuje prema početnom roku, roku produženja i otkaznom roku. Ako je početni rok 12 meseci, a otkazni rok 3 meseca, rok za dostavljanje otkaza ističe 9 meseci od početka ugovora. Ako je rok produženja 12 meseci, ovaj datum se pomera za još 12 meseci.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Cancellation Possible Until - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the value of the Contract Line No. field.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Contract Line No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the contract to which the Subscription Line is to be assigned.
trans-unit.target: Određuje ugovor kojem će red pretplate biti dodeljen.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Contract No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the currency of amounts in the Subscription Line.
trans-unit.target: Određuje valutu iznosa u redu pretplate.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Currency Code - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the currency factor valid for the Subscription Line, which is used to convert amounts to the client currency.
trans-unit.target: Određuje važeći faktor valute za red pretplate, koji se koristi za preračunavanje iznosa u valutu kupca.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Currency Factor - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the date when the currency factor was last updated.
trans-unit.target: Određuje datum kada je faktor valute poslednji put ažuriran.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Currency Factor Date - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the description of the Subscription Line.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Description - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the value of the Dimension Set ID field.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Dimension Set ID - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether the Subscription Line is used as a basis for periodic invoicing or discounts.
trans-unit.target: Određuje da li se red pretplate koristi kao osnova za periodično fakturisanje ili popuste.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Discount - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the percent of the discount for the Subscription Line.
trans-unit.target: Određuje procenat popusta za red pretplate.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Discount % - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the amount of the discount for the Subscription Line.
trans-unit.target: Određuje iznos popusta za red pretplate.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Discount Amount - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the discount amount in client currency that is granted on the Subscription Line.
trans-unit.target: Određuje iznos popusta u valuti kupca koji se odobrava na red pretplate.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Discount Amount (LCY) - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the number of the entry assigned to it from the specified number series when it was created.
trans-unit.target: Određuje broj stavke koji je dodeljen iz navedene brojčane serije pri kreiranju.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Entry No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies a date formula for automatic renewal after initial term and the rhythm of the update of "Notice possible to" and "Term Until". If the field is empty and the initial term or notice period is filled, the end of Subscription Line is automatically set to the end of the initial term or notice period.
trans-unit.target: Određuje formulu datuma za automatsku obnovu nakon početnog roka i ritam ažuriranja polja "Otkaz moguć do” i "Važi do”. Ako je polje prazno, a početni rok ili otkazni rok popunjen, kraj reda pretplate se automatski postavlja na kraj početnog roka ili otkaznog roka.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Extension Term - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies a date formula for calculating the minimum term of the Subscription Line. If the minimum term is filled and no extension term is entered, the end of Subscription Line is automatically set to the end of the initial term.
trans-unit.target: Određuje formulu datuma za izračunavanje minimalnog roka reda pretplate. Ako je minimalni rok popunjen, a rok produženja nije unet, kraj reda pretplate se automatski postavlja na kraj početnog roka.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Initial Term - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the value of the Invoicing Item No. field.
trans-unit.target: Određuje vrednost polja "Br. artikla za fakturisanje”.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Invoicing Item No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the monthly recurring amount in local currency.
trans-unit.target: Određuje mesečni ponavljajući iznos u lokalnoj valuti.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Monthly Recurr. Revenue (LCY) - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the monthly recurring costs in local currency.
trans-unit.target: Određuje mesečne ponavljajuće troškove u lokalnoj valuti.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Monthly Recurring Cost (LCY) - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the date of the next billing possible.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Next Billing Date - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies a date formula for the lead time that a notice must have before the Subscription Line ends. The rhythm of the update of "Notice possible to" and "Term Until" is determined using the extension term. For example, with an extension period of 1M, the notice period is repeatedly postponed by one month.
trans-unit.target: Određuje formulu datuma za vremenski period unapred koji otkaz mora imati pre završetka reda pretplate. Ritam ažuriranja polja "Otkaz moguć do” i "Važi do” određuje se putem roka produženja. Na primer, uz rok produženja 1M, otkazni rok se svaki put pomera za jedan mesec.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Notice Period - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the code of the Subscription Package. If a Vendor Subscription Contract line has the same Subscription No. and Package Code as a Customer Subscription Contract line, the Customer Subscription Contract dimension value is copied to the Vendor Subscription Contract line.
trans-unit.target: Određuje šifru pretplatničkog paketa.. Ako red pretplatničkog ugovora sa dobavljačem ima isti br. pretplate i šifru paketa kao red pretplatničkog ugovora sa kupcem, vrednost dimenzije sa pretplatničkog ugovora sa kupcem kopira se u red pretplatničkog ugovora sa dobavljačem.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Package Code - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether the Subscription Line will will be calculated as a credit (Purchase Invoice) or as debit (Sales Invoice).
trans-unit.target: Određuje da li će se red pretplate obračunavati kao potraživanje (nabavna faktura) ili kao zaduženje (prodajna faktura).
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Partner - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the number of the partner who will receive the contract components and be billed by default.
trans-unit.target: Određuje broj partnera koji će podrazumevano primati elemente ugovora i kome će se fakturisati.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Partner No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the price of the Subscription Line with quantity of 1 in the billing period. The price is calculated from Base Price and Base Price %.
trans-unit.target: Određuje cenu reda pretplate za količinu 1 u periodu fakturisanja. Cena se izračunava iz osnovne cene i procenta osnovne cene.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Price - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the price of the Subscription Line in client currency related to quantity of 1 in the billing period. The price is calculated from Base Price and Base Price %.
trans-unit.target: Određuje cenu reda pretplate u valuti kupca za količinu 1 u periodu fakturisanja. Cena se izračunava iz osnovne cene i procenta osnovne cene.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Price (LCY) - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the value of the Quantity field.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Quantity Decimal - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies a date formula by which the Contract Line is renewed and the end of the Contract Line is extended. It is automatically preset with the initial term of the Subscription Line and can be changed manually.
trans-unit.target: Određuje formulu datuma po kojoj se red ugovora obnavlja i produžava mu se kraj. Automatski se unapred popunjava početnim rokom reda pretplate i može se ručno izmeniti.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Renewal Term - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the amount for the Subscription Line including discount.
trans-unit.target: Određuje iznos za red pretplate, uključujući popust.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Amount - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the amount in client currency for the Subscription Line including discount.
trans-unit.target: Određuje iznos u valuti klijenta za red pretplate, uključujući popust.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Amount (LCY) - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the value of the Subscription Line Line No. field.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Commitment Entry No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the date up to which the Subscription Line is valid.
trans-unit.target: Određuje datum do kog red pretplate važi.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service End Date - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the value of the Subscription Description field.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Object Description - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the Item No. of the Subscription.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Object Item No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the contract to which the Subscription Line is to be assigned.
trans-unit.target: Određuje ugovor kojem će red pretplate biti dodeljen.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Object No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the Source No. of the Subscription.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Object Source No. - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the Source Type of the Subscription.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Object Source Type - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the date from which the Subscription Line is valid and will be invoiced.
trans-unit.target: Određuje datum od kog je red pretplate važeći i biće fakturisan.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Service Start Date - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the code of the Subscription Package Line Template.
trans-unit.target: Određuje šifru obrasca reda pretplatničkog paketa.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Template - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the earliest regular date for the end of the Subscription Line, taking into account the initial term, extension term and a notice period. An initial term of 24 months results in a fixed term of 2 years. An extension period of 12 months postpones this date by 12 months.
trans-unit.target: Određuje najraniji redovni datum završetka reda pretplate, uzimajući u obzir početni rok, rok produženja i otkazni rok. Početni rok od 24 meseca daje fiksni rok od 2 godine. Rok produženja od 12 meseci pomera ovaj datum za 12 meseci.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Term Until - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies the unit cost of the item.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Unit Cost (LCY) - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether usage data is used as the basis for billing via contracts.
trans-unit.target: Određuje da li se podaci o korišćenju koriste kao osnova za fakturisanje preko ugovora.
trans-unit.note: Page Contract Analysis Entries - Control Usage Based Billing - Property ToolTip
